_:N5a12a4520621435c982cdd3331c76c14 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Preet Kaur Gill was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department of Health and Social Care on 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Birmingham Edgbaston in June 2017.</p>\n" .
